				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You've got a peak MIPS count of ~1.8 on the S-CPU. I haven't heard of any vorbis/mp3 decoder implementations that come even close to meeting that sort of performance constraint, even on far more capable processors.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

